item.title: About
item.description: Summary Jimmy Tang is a HPC SRE at Voysis. He has worked at Logentries within Rapid7, Quantum Biosystems, Digital Repository of Ireland and a number of grid storage systems in the HPC Europa 1 and 2 programs, developing management and storage solutions for numerical computing. He has also participated in the development and deployment of the infrastructure for the Irish African Partnership, 1641 Depositions, IITAC, eINIS and a number of other research projects.
